# SwiftUI Component Patterns — React & React Native

## React Native — NativeWind SwiftUI-Klassen
Wenn React Native + NativeWind: diese Klassen bevorzugen:

### Card (iOS Grouped List Card)
className="bg-white rounded-xl mx-4 overflow-hidden
           border border-black/5"

### Primary Button (iOS Filled Button)
className="bg-blue-500 rounded-[10px] h-[50px] px-6
           items-center justify-center active:scale-95"
Text: className="text-white font-semibold text-[17px]"

### Input (iOS Text Field)
className="h-[44px] bg-[#F2F2F7] rounded-[10px] px-4
           text-[17px] font-normal"

### Navigation Large Title
className="text-[34px] font-bold text-black px-4 pt-2 pb-1"

### List Row
className="flex-row items-center px-4 h-[44px] bg-white
           border-b border-black/[0.08]"

### Tab Bar Icon (aktiv)
className="text-[#007AFF]" size={24}

## React (Web) — SwiftUI-Look mit Tailwind
Tailwind-Config muss diese Custom-Tokens haben:

### tailwind.config.ts Ergänzung
extend: {
  colors: {
    'sf-blue':   '#007AFF',
    'sf-green':  '#34C759',
    'sf-red':    '#FF3B30',
    'sf-orange': '#FF9500',
    'sf-gray1':  '#8E8E93',
    'sf-gray6':  '#F2F2F7',
    'sf-sep':    'rgba(60,60,67,0.12)',
  },
  borderRadius: {
    'ios-card':   '12px',
    'ios-btn':    '10px',
    'ios-input':  '10px',
    'ios-modal':  '16px',
  },
  fontFamily: {
    'sf': ['-apple-system', 'BlinkMacSystemFont', '"SF Pro Display"',
           '"SF Pro Text"', 'Inter', 'sans-serif'],
  },
  transitionTimingFunction: {
    'ios': 'cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94)',
  }
}

## iOS Sheet Modal (React)
- Position: fixed bottom-0, volle Breite
- Handle: 36x4px, grau, border-radius 2px, oben zentriert, 8px margin
- Hintergrund: weiß, border-radius 16px 16px 0 0
- Animation: translateY(100%) → translateY(0), iOS-Kurve, 0.3s

## Spacing-Regel
IMMER SF-Spacing-Scale nutzen: 4, 8, 12, 16, 20, 24, 32, 40, 48px
Kein freies Spacing wie 15px, 22px, 37px — nicht iOS-nativ

## Schriften-Hierarchie
- Large Title:  34px / 700 / -0.4px letter-spacing
- Title 1:      28px / 700
- Title 2:      22px / 700
- Title 3:      20px / 600
- Headline:     17px / 600
- Body:         17px / 400
- Callout:      16px / 400
- Subheadline:  15px / 400
- Footnote:     13px / 400
- Caption:      12px / 400
